{"tid":1956651,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"作左首歌屌鳩中共出口武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-04-03T10:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T08:00:47.000Z","uid":100700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"127a2c885f64fa5b48af019424f8cec6af8cec83","tid":1956651,"uid":100700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">每個年代都會有自己既歌記錄返當刻發生既事，依加中共係咁打資訊戰嘗試為自己洗底，我諗大家都嬲到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟作左首歌屌鳩中共、港共，同細胃，希望將呢段歷史用音樂記低。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[url]Link: <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/moonbus-846175750/moonbus[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fmoonbus-846175750%2Fmoonbus%5B%2Furl%5D&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=b4766cad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/moonbus-846175750/moonbus[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n 圍籬的韭菜<br />\n曲: 月巴MoonBus<br />\n詞: 積孽廢青 @alexanderhui<br />\nBass: 阿智<br />\nCredit: 立場新聞 蘋果日報 有線新聞 伍正文<br />\n<br />\n輸出死症大條道理 佢地<br />\n穿梭歐美殺人歷遍 各地<br />\n笠返口罩繼續隔離<br />\n我先得廿歲人未想死<br />\n如同在戰地<br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠孔雀駱駝食晒 惹味<br />\n要揾錢佢直頭沒有 禁忌<br />\n總於知道死嘅滋味<br />\n玻璃心到要全球攬炒 仲要多謝佢地<br />\n<br />\n維尼的狗德塞姓譚 何時先可釘蓋<br />\n話要帶領世衛 結局已知 絕對可一不可再<br />\n明明講好可控 突然全球開始失控<br />\n完全當佢冇事 愛護習帝千載千千載 「半封關 冇事 信政府～」<br />\n總猜不透777的構思<br />\n全人類每日仍舊 返工放飯<br />\n繼續期待 總有新開始<br />\n要死不去才是意義"},{"pid":"7388019f8d5fc5b3546410ae175422ec472a2b7d","tid":1956651,"uid":100700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"補link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/moonbus-846175750/moonbus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fmoonbus-846175750%2Fmoonbus&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=275d245b\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/moonbus-846175750/moonbus</a>"},{"pid":"4a04e4392bf4252ade4ab9c51f1343029d9e10d4","tid":1956651,"uid":100700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r